      • getCancelled

        @Nonnull
T getCancelled(boolean hasBeenCancelled)
        Creates a narrowed-down, independent collection of disbursement data for disbursements that have been cancelled. Notice that checking disbursement status here is not the best option, as the disbursement might be in a temporary state (QC-Held) while it is know that it will be cancelled (cancellation reason != null).
        Parameters:
        hasBeenCancelled - true iff disbursements that have been cancelled must be selected.
        Returns:
        the new collection.
